data.description:
Looking for a charming and cozy place to call home? Look no further than this cute-as-a-button house on a corner lot! With 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home is the perfect size for a small family or anyone looking to downsize.
Step inside and be greeted by a formal living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing after a long day. The oversized master bedroom provides plenty of space to stretch out and unwind, while the new granite countertops in the kitchen are a beautiful and functional addition.
But that's not all - this home also boasts a brand new hot water heater and roof, ensuring that you can move in with peace of mind. And with a corner lot location, you'll enjoy plenty of privacy and outdoor space to enjoy the beautiful surroundings.
Don't miss your chance to make this adorable house your forever home - schedule a showing today!
